Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:34.21,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:36.12,DCMain,YOKOMIZO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Can I say it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:40.04,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.12,0:24:37.24,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah, go ahead.
